text: Heini Ihle (born 24 April 1941) is a German ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of West Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Oberstdorf
